{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Unless we do something to prevent it,"},{"time":2000,"text":"over the next 40 years we’re facing an epidemic"},{"time":5000,"text":"of neurologic diseases on a global scale."},{"time":8000,"text":"A cheery thought."},{"time":12000,"text":"On this map, every country that’s colored blue"},{"time":15000,"text":"has more than 20 percent of its population over the age of 65."},{"time":19000,"text":"This is the world we live in."},{"time":21000,"text":"And this is the world your children will live in."},{"time":25000,"text":"For 12,000 years, the distribution of ages in the human population"},{"time":29000,"text":"has looked like a pyramid, with the oldest on top."},{"time":32000,"text":"It’s already flattening out."},{"time":34000,"text":"By 2050, it’s going to be a column and will start to invert."},{"time":38000,"text":"This is why it’s happening."},{"time":41000,"text":"The average lifespan’s more than doubled since 1840,"},{"time":44000,"text":"and it’s increasing currently at the rate of about five hours every day."},{"time":49000,"text":"And this is why that’s not entirely a good thing:"},{"time":52000,"text":"because over the age of 65, your risk of getting Alzheimer’s"},{"time":56000,"text":"or Parkinson’s disease will increase exponentially."},{"time":60000,"text":"By 2050, there’ll be about 32 million people in the United States"},{"time":64000,"text":"over the age of 80, and unless we do something about it,"},{"time":67000,"text":"half of them will have Alzheimer’s disease"},{"time":69000,"text":"and three million more will have Parkinson’s disease."},{"time":72000,"text":"Right now, those and other neurologic diseases --"},{"time":75000,"text":"for which we have no cure or prevention --"},{"time":78000,"text":"cost about a third of a trillion dollars a year."},{"time":80000,"text":"It will be well over a trillion dollars by 2050."},{"time":84000,"text":"Alzheimer’s disease starts when a protein"},{"time":86000,"text":"that should be folded up properly"},{"time":88000,"text":"misfolds into a kind of demented origami."},{"time":92000,"text":"So one approach we’re taking is to try to design drugs"},{"time":95000,"text":"that function like molecular Scotch tape,"},{"time":98000,"text":"to hold the protein into its proper shape."},{"time":101000,"text":"That would keep it from forming the tangles"},{"time":103000,"text":"that seem to kill large sections of the brain when they do."},{"time":107000,"text":"Interestingly enough, other neurologic diseases"},{"time":109000,"text":"which affect very different parts of the brain"},{"time":112000,"text":"also show tangles of misfolded protein,"},{"time":115000,"text":"which suggests that the approach might be a general one,"},{"time":118000,"text":"and might be used to cure many neurologic diseases,"},{"time":120000,"text":"not just Alzheimer’s disease."},{"time":122000,"text":"There’s also a fascinating connection to cancer here,"},{"time":125000,"text":"because people with neurologic diseases"},{"time":127000,"text":"have a very low incidence of most cancers."},{"time":130000,"text":"And this is a connection that most people aren’t pursuing right now,"},{"time":133000,"text":"but which we’re fascinated by."},{"time":136000,"text":"Most of the important and all of the creative work in this area"},{"time":139000,"text":"is being funded by private philanthropies."},{"time":142000,"text":"And there’s tremendous scope for additional private help here,"},{"time":145000,"text":"because the government has dropped the ball on much of this, I’m afraid."},{"time":148000,"text":"In the meantime, while we’re waiting for all these things to happen,"},{"time":152000,"text":"here’s what you can do for yourself."},{"time":154000,"text":"If you want to lower your risk of Parkinson’s disease,"},{"time":156000,"text":"caffeine is protective to some extent; nobody knows why."},{"time":161000,"text":"Head injuries are bad for you. They lead to Parkinson’s disease."},{"time":164000,"text":"And the Avian Flu is also not a good idea."},{"time":169000,"text":"As far as protecting yourself against Alzheimer’s disease,"},{"time":172000,"text":"well, it turns out that fish oil has the effect"},{"time":175000,"text":"of reducing your risk for Alzheimer’s disease."},{"time":178000,"text":"You should also keep your blood pressure down,"},{"time":180000,"text":"because chronic high blood pressure"},{"time":182000,"text":"is the biggest single risk factor for Alzheimer’s disease."},{"time":184000,"text":"It’s also the biggest risk factor for glaucoma,"},{"time":187000,"text":"which is just Alzheimer’s disease of the eye."},{"time":190000,"text":"And of course, when it comes to cognitive effects,"},{"time":192000,"text":"\"use it or lose it\" applies,"},{"time":194000,"text":"so you want to stay mentally stimulated."},{"time":196000,"text":"But hey, you’re listening to me."},{"time":198000,"text":"So you’ve got that covered."},{"time":200000,"text":"And one final thing. Wish people like me luck, okay?"},{"time":204000,"text":"Because the clock is ticking for all of us."},{"time":206000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}